Does he have a chronic illness?

263
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:01,810
Goriki Clinic

264
00:16:01,810 --> 00:16:03,610
Go check it out.

265
00:16:08,990 --> 00:16:10,910
Is this really an investigation?

266
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:12,940
Why are you alone?

267
00:16:13,450 --> 00:16:15,190
It's simple.

268
00:16:15,190 --> 00:16:17,540
If you've got nothing to hide,
