269
00:16:35,650 --> 00:16:39,060
This dash cam allows you to film
the inside of your vehicle, doesn't it?

270
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:40,370
That's right.

271
00:16:40,370 --> 00:16:41,910
How long do you store your recordings?

272
00:16:41,910 --> 00:16:44,700
About two weeks.

273
