She'll be on here, then.

274
00:16:48,420 --> 00:16:49,450
What?

275
00:16:49,450 --> 00:16:53,080
That missing high school
girl got in your car.

276
00:16:53,890 --> 00:16:55,050
My car?

277
00:16:55,050 --> 00:16:59,340
I'm taking your data. This is a seizure.

278
00:17:00,190 --> 00:17:02,850
If anything comes up,
I expect your cooperation again.

279
00:17:02,850 --> 00:17:06,650
Don't go to the police, though.

280
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:11,530
Hello, ma'am.

281
00:17:11,530 --> 00:17:12,450
Hello.

282
00:17:12,450 --> 00:17:13,500
Hello.

283
00:17:15,730 --> 00:17:20,820
Taeko-san was right. He doesn't
seem like an ordinary taxi driver.

284
00:17:22,140 --> 00:17:23,610
I'm back.

285
00:17:23,610 --> 00:17:24,450
Welcome back.

286
00:17:24,450 --> 00:17:25,190
Welcome back.

287
00:17:25,190 --> 00:17:27,900
Any developments in the missing
high school girl case?

288
00:17:27,900 --> 00:17:29,880
It's all over the news.

289
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:32,380
Yeah, because her life's in danger.

290
00:17:32,730 --> 00:17:35,580
The media started
receiving information today.

291
