Just after 1 AM two days ago on the 4th,

292
00:17:39,510 --> 00:17:42,910
after doing some shopping at a
convenience store, she got in a taxi.

293
00:17:43,930 --> 00:17:46,750
Have they identified the taxi?

294
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:49,080
Apparently the clerk remembered the number.

295
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:51,480
Huh? After seeing it only once and briefly?

296
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:55,660
It happened to be their birthday, 1022.

297
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:57,390
What?

298
00:17:57,390 --> 00:17:59,210
Wow.

299
00:18:09,650 --> 00:18:14,030
A high school girl has gone missing
in Nerima City, Tokyo.

300
00:18:14,690 --> 00:18:17,620
She has been unreachable
since she left her home late at night

301
00:18:17,620 --> 00:18:19,080
two days ago on the 4th of this month.

302
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:21,730
The next morning, her family…

303
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:26,750
We, the Homosapiens, just received
the results of Round 1 of the N-1.

304
00:18:26,750 --> 00:18:28,260
And would you believe it? We passed!

305
00:18:28,260 --> 00:18:29,350
Of course we did.

306
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:31,050
Even amateurs could make it past Round 1.

307
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:32,890
Where do you think the finish line is?

308
00:18:31,300 --> 00:18:38,800
Equator Sauna

309
00:18:32,890 --> 00:18:35,100
But last year, we failed in Round 2.

310
00:18:35,100 --> 00:18:36,400
After ten years in the business...

311
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:45,560
Equator Sauna

312
00:18:52,460 --> 00:18:53,570
Who is it?

313
00:18:53,570 --> 00:18:55,870
We work for Ibusuki.

314
00:19:03,890 --> 00:19:05,120
Hello.

315
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,280
Hello.

316
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:13,870
You look young. Have a seat.

317
00:19:13,870 --> 00:19:15,100
Excuse us.

318
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:19,660
So?

319
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:26,950
We need a remote monitoring
dash cam and GPS installed.

320
00:19:26,950 --> 00:19:30,810
What? Hold on. That's totally illegal.

321
00:19:30,810 --> 00:19:32,510
Where?

322
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:37,740
His car. This is the dash cam.

323
00:19:41,020 --> 00:19:42,640
It's a common model.

324
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:44,660
You'll install it, won't you?

325
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:47,020
If you pay for it.

326
00:19:47,410 --> 00:19:48,730
You'll be paid tomorrow.

327
00:19:48,730 --> 00:19:53,450
No can do. Equator operates 24 hours
a day, but that's just the sauna.

328
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:55,800
How long will it take?

329
00:19:55,800 --> 00:19:59,120
I'm busy. Give me three days.

330
00:19:59,120 --> 00:20:00,840
Make it one.

331
00:20:01,630 --> 00:20:05,330
1.5 days, or pay a rush late night surcharge.

332
00:20:06,030 --> 00:20:06,940
How much?

333
00:20:06,940 --> 00:20:11,410
550,000. And I'll need your help, too.

334
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:19,620
Pretty old car.
Didn't need all these tools.

335
00:20:27,910 --> 00:20:30,040
How long will it take?

336
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:34,700
About seven or eight minutes.

337
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:36,080
Seven or eight minutes?

338
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:37,010
Yeah.

339
00:20:47,010 --> 00:20:48,080
What is it?

340
00:20:49,630 --> 00:20:51,140
Are you hungry?

341
00:20:52,400 --> 00:20:53,740
Hold on.

342
00:20:59,520 --> 00:21:01,490
Okay, all good.

343
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:08,810
That should do it.

344
00:21:09,130 --> 00:21:13,970
Fine. I'll go buy you something.
Stay put and be good.

345
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:23,320
Crap, crap, crap.

346
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:27,020
Odokawa's coming, Odokawa's
coming, Odokawa's coming!

347
00:21:27,020 --> 00:21:28,700
Crap, crap, crap!

348
00:21:28,700 --> 00:21:30,160
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

349
00:21:34,250 --> 00:21:36,200
Was he really talking to someone?

350
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:41,240
Yeah. He even ominously told them
to “stay put and be good.”

351
00:21:43,970 --> 00:21:49,980
Anyway, I could imagine him kidnapping
and holding someone as cute as her

352
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:52,710
if she happened to get in his taxi.

353
00:21:52,710 --> 00:21:56,940
He may be involved, but kidnapping
 and false imprisonment?

354
00:21:57,840 --> 00:21:59,430
No, you're right. I guess not.

355
00:22:01,730 --> 00:22:04,170
Did you call her cute?

356
00:22:05,630 --> 00:22:07,670
Did I say that?

357
00:22:07,670 --> 00:22:10,970
Yeah, didn't you just say that?

358
00:22:12,820 --> 00:22:14,410
No, you definitely did.

359
00:22:14,410 --> 00:22:14,860
What?

360
00:22:14,860 --> 00:22:17,410
Her photo hasn't appeared on the news yet.

361
00:22:17,410 --> 00:22:18,930
Why'd you say that?

362
00:22:18,930 --> 00:22:19,780
I didn't say that.

363
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:20,910
No, you did.

364
00:22:22,250 --> 00:22:24,430
What? Really?

365
00:22:24,430 --> 00:22:25,180
Yeah.

366
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:31,270
I caught a glimpse of the boss' documents.

367
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:32,190
I knew it.

368
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:36,600
They were out in the open on his desk.

369
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:37,800
Hold on.

370
00:22:38,890 --> 00:22:39,650
Hey.

371
00:22:39,650 --> 00:22:40,550
Where'd they go?

372
00:22:40,550 --> 00:22:41,940
Don't go through his stuff.

373
00:22:41,940 --> 00:22:43,050
This is it.

374
00:22:43,530 --> 00:22:44,250
Don't.

375
00:22:44,250 --> 00:22:45,650
Wait, wait, wait.

376
00:22:46,360 --> 00:22:47,470
Look at this Buddha.

377
00:22:47,470 --> 00:22:50,000
Tada! A Buddha.

378
00:22:50,740 --> 00:22:52,060
Wait a minute.

379
00:22:55,130 --> 00:22:56,400
Mitsuya?

380
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:58,980
This is Yuki.

381
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:01,860
Mitsuya-san.

382
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:16,300
Next Time

383
00:23:01,860 --> 00:23:03,280
Have we met?

