387
00:23:09,830 --> 00:23:11,580
You should stay away from them.

388
00:23:11,580 --> 00:23:12,900
You're cute, too, Rena-san.

389
00:23:12,530 --> 00:23:15,900
This show is a work of fiction.

390
00:23:12,900 --> 00:23:13,580
What?

391
00:23:13,580 --> 00:23:15,870
I told you, I won't work for you.

